{"about_the_game":"<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start\uff1a</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hearthstone? Slay the Spire? Blackjack?<br>To be precise, it's Blackjack in the roguelike mode of <i>Slay the Spire</i>, with a board inspired by <i>Hearthstone</i>. If you're familiar with them, you'll find this game easy to pick up.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Classic Gameplay:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Based on playing cards, players take turns drawing cards, with the goal of getting as close to 21 points as possible. The player closest to 21 wins, but exceeding 21 causes an automatic bust and results in a loss. Both players will take damage equal to the difference in card values, until one defeats the other or is defeated themselves.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Class Selection:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players will choose their starting class, which will define their role in the game. Each class comes with its own unique deck and abilities, as well as two talent branches. Each branch offers different card builds, allowing for varied playstyles and strategies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/extras/zhiye-steam-E.png?t=1737188324\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rich Roguelike Elements:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players will build their own deck from over 300 cards, with the added twist of random events that can introduce new cards, refine their deck, or even forge powerful cards. These choices are all influenced by the chips you win at the table, which will be key to your path to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/extras/kabai-steam-Y.png?t=1737188324\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple Choices:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The map is designed based on <i>Slay the Spire</i>, allowing players to freely choose their encounter paths. Each floor presents different opponents and events, so you might need specific enemies or card sets to progress, or you could choose to power through everything to the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/extras/dituzhongzi-steam-ZYE.png?t=1737188324\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Card types, forge and upgrade:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/extras/duanzao-steam-Y.png?t=1737188324\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">reverse side of the card\uff1a</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/extras/kabei-steam-E.png?t=1737188324\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plan\uff1a</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/extras/kaifajihua-steam-E.png?t=1737188324\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737188324","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/page.bg.jpg?t=1737188324","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/f8ab6d8c749a0fefb64e16b6ef73402a2ecf17f9/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737188324","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262580/f8ab6d8c749a0fefb64e16b6ef73402a2ecf17f9/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737188324","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids